description.en: $GOON is a token that embodies the essence of crypto trading.  By idolizing the one who's made a life retirement from crypto, the idea of $GOON is to prove that anybody can do it.  In creating a platform that will both hosted with it's own NFT platform on onlymemes.com, this token will serve as the pilot for onboarding crypto creators and presences in the space.  We started with the most known and hyped trader, GoonRich and have already received an amazing amount of volume.
